data.title: County of Werdenberg
data.text:
County of Werdenberg-Sargans-Sargansball was a Holy Roman Imperial countyball.

History

County of Werdenberg-Sargans-Sargansball started back when it was a 2ball, then they form Germaniaball, then after the Romans collapse, the Germans (germanics) spreaded into Western Europe, then the Frankish Empireball came along, then forming the HREball.
